column16: Xander Bogaerts homers (1) on a fly ball to left center field.   Jackie Bradley Jr.   scores.
Ryan Lavarnway flies out sharply to center fielder Brett Gardner.
Will Middlebrooks lines out to right fielder Ichiro Suzuki.
Mike Napoli flies out to left fielder Alfonso Soriano.
David Ortiz out on a sacrifice fly to center fielder Brett Gardner.   Jonny Gomes scores.    Dustin Pedroia to 3rd.
Dustin Pedroia doubles (38) on a sharp line drive to left fielder Alfonso Soriano.   Jonny Gomes to 3rd.
Jonny Gomes singles on a line drive to center fielder Brett Gardner.   Shane Victorino scores.
